{"tid":375500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實澳門狗 有冇諗過係上天比警告你地 賭場雞竇令幾多人家破人亡","createTime":"2017-08-26T14:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T01:06:02.000Z","uid":54373,"like":80,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c56398b1ae4c2928597719974d448125f32b94","tid":375500,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:00:30.000Z","msg":"黃色事業,已經唔洗講<br />\n<br />\n賭係最陰質的一個行業<br />\n<br />\n你地既賭業,基本上係全民參與<br />\n政府靠賭稅生存<br />\n全民都有玩賭廳d人集資,變相都係全城害人<br />\n<br />\n報應而家先來"},{"pid":"accb21255e8681d3aabe43dc19463de5fc2a871b","tid":375500,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:01:57.000Z","msg":"天滅凹狗🐕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ff0987cc6c1f8cf5221f69e2a7dad5891080f9","tid":375500,"uid":94828,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:02:59.000Z","msg":"都算佢地基建夠垃圾先會中招既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d967ca77cd44d09122fb37abe24d5b40b90ee3","tid":375500,"uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"淨空法師 2007年<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">賭博就是占人家便宜！這是在佛法裡頭決定禁止的，不可以賭，賭博的念頭是盜心，用這種不正當的手段奪取別人的財物</span>，盜心。佛菩薩教誨我們，所有宗教神明都教給我們，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不義之財</span></span>決定不能取。不義是什麼？不應該得到的。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不義之財你要得到了，往往有很難想像的災難，這個事情古今中外都有，都很多。</span></span>中國古聖先賢苦口婆心勸導大家，安分守己，積德修善，唯有這樣，大家的前途才一片光明。哪一個人發財是靠賭博起家的？哪一個人發財是靠偷竊起家的？古今中外找不到，我們要明了這個道理，知道事實真相。佛菩薩常常教給我們，安貧樂道，知足常樂。許多人因為賭博而傾家蕩產、離婚、自殺，造成嚴重的社會問題。所以，沒有一個宗教不禁止賭博的，我們在其他宗教典籍裡面都能看到。有同修問我，為了不掃朋友的興，而陪朋友去賭場賭博，是不是犯戒？為了人情，陪著人去賭博，確實是犯戒。古德常常教我們，不把佛事當人情。你要是陪朋友賭博，你有能力把這些賭博的朋友，統統都把他轉過頭來學佛，這行！這是你的善巧方便，是你度眾生一套本事，可以。如果你度不了他，就決定不隨緣；能夠度得了，可以隨緣，這是四攝法裡頭的&ldquo;同事攝&rdquo;。怕的是你度不了他，反而是他把你度了，這就壞了，所以最好不陪朋友們做這些事情。 <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n    又有些同修，他們希望發橫財來幫助佛教，這是妄想。佛教的事業自然有佛菩薩加持，用不著打這個妄想；打這個妄想，破壞你自己的功夫。 <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n    有人問我，世間人喜歡賭博，那些人什麼時候會回頭？物極必反，你不要著急，讓他去賭，輸到他家產盡光的時候，他就回頭。開賭場的，用賭博這種方式來賺人家的錢，他能不能發財？不能，這裡頭因果的道理要懂。設很多圈套，把人家錢奪來，他能發得了財嗎？哪有這種道理！如<span style=\"color: red;\">果這樣可以發財，釋迦牟尼佛早就開賭場了，沒有這個道理。</span>你騙來的也好，搶來的也好，用什麼方法奪取的都好，都是你命裡所有的。你命裡沒有，無論你用什麼方法，你還是發不了財。你不相信，你去開賭場，他開賭場賺錢，你開賭場一定蝕本。為什麼？沒有命！用賭博這種不好的方法叫別人破產，他自己發財；這個發財的人，他的財庫本來就很豐足。譬如，他的財富有一萬個億那麼大的財富，他開設賭場賺錢，他的一生所賺大概只有五千個億，打對折了。為什麼？造惡，虧折了。佛告訴我們事實真相，這我們在講席裡頭常講，還得常常提醒。為什麼？你健忘，你迷惑。"},{"pid":"cbf7867b7692ce6483b5382d005a404246a6fa82","tid":375500,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:05:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e65873d7f3a42f97d58b00244231e10d30ca6ab5","tid":375500,"uid":47147,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d11a292b82757b4e85371d58f571919265e592e","tid":375500,"uid":74281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"澳門狗比天收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eac1e2fe7ada5998339a39ab0ce59d0201aa67d","tid":375500,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:13:33.000Z","msg":"一個廳爆已經咁多苦主<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">跟本全民參與賭博,不義之財,必得報應!</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/recommend/20151001/271997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Frecommend%2F20151001%2F271997&d=oprbwUJw99tpXiQ1ARWMI0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e26c0c1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Frecommend%2F20151001%2F271997&h=f2e9af21\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/recommend/20151001/271997</a><br />\n<br />\n賭業崩潰】多金唔見20億 苦主喊圍永利<br />\n<br />\n上週四，大批苦主帶齊橫額在永利酒店門外抗議，橫額更寫上向華強名字，他們除批評向華強不予理會外，也批評澳門政府對賭廳監察不力，未有協助苦主解決事件。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名六十歲苦主游先生，三月時向家人集資了三十萬，每月利息達六千元，直到八月，他一直也收到利息。他說出事後，每晚都失眠，力斥對方無人性，希望政府和永利負責承擔他損失。而五十七歲做疊碼的田姐告訴記者，她二月時存了三百萬到賭廳，「筆錢係用間屋抵押出來嘅資本，每月需還款兩萬多，依家都唔知點算。」"},{"pid":"1a7927cc9a87ce6cb6ad3a49a1c3c2a04571631d","tid":375500,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:15:05.000Z","msg":"報應呀報應呀！"},{"pid":"5dfc581b95c2bb0d4346ab988f8412275052d7d2","tid":375500,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:17:34.000Z","msg":"見好多澳門狗都拜佛,好多都係搵到錢做賭既人<br />\n<br />\n知唔知,<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你做賭,佛祖已經唔會保佑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"352552ab2a1667c3bbf782434f1a3fad02b6b0ac","tid":375500,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:17:50.000Z","msg":"咁計香港真係黑錢天堂wo"},{"pid":"2fd53e842046331341aefade5f57b1ae5c2dd237","tid":375500,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832bd27a1a0d8fc4e072166bc0f9757497181f20","tid":375500,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁計香港真係黑錢天堂wo</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪一路都受緊共撚黨管治下嘅人禍囉"},{"pid":"a8984ab3b7a45ad760867d7ebc32eab202fbfec4","tid":375500,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"935aabc49a80a431d4f0a6413e484a34f3dfc847","tid":375500,"uid":28800,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c582a81350cb719aea054dd6e517940cd5f70594","tid":375500,"uid":43842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見好多澳門狗都拜佛,好多都係搵到錢做賭既人<br />\n<br />\n知唔知,<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你做賭,佛祖已經唔會保佑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n佛祖係會保佑每一個人 只會你信<br />\n但係自己業力最終都要自己受返 <br />\n避得一時 避唔到一世"},{"pid":"6cc0e425f1339792247ef8d5ead143e1e39025c3","tid":375500,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:53:04.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n孽障有排佢還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿彌陀佛~~"},{"pid":"141cc9c5e5eb50000bf78c04584cd8416f621aa9","tid":375500,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:19:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n孽障有排佢還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿彌陀佛~~</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a872c8f456c4ce5767e7c9158deeed4c41dce817","tid":375500,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49b650ad2e29e80f3e35276f43241e903aad618","tid":375500,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/192647_8de4cbf77d084bad139d6e54a83d28bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F192647_8de4cbf77d084bad139d6e54a83d28bd.jpg&h=515fda4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cda4c08c8b80564a3541a5efeffa48d237160e20","tid":375500,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞就邊度都有得叫 唔係得澳門<br />\n<br />\n香港夠有馬會 一樣大把人輸到死<br />\n<br />\n同埋係澳門賭錢整大部份都唔係本地人<br />\n<br />\n因為澳門人好多都知道賭係會家破人亡</blockquote><br />\n你母親都係私家雞"},{"pid":"113224a13b310f0a9ce48bab660893c57a879ebf","tid":375500,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:13:22.000Z","msg":"其實香港都差唔多<br />\n炒炒炒，得金融 冇實業"},{"pid":"58f9b4d985a68dab3cbdafa766c052afc68a39f3","tid":375500,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實香港都差唔多<br />\n炒炒炒，得金融 冇實業</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你當物流業死架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"33b04460554a1844645e96a3e8d093992f88f8f1","tid":375500,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T19:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁香港既賽狗會呢?</blockquote><br />\n啲錢好多都係慈善公益用途點同姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3171bd95ea05147b028e33c02bed3b2109fc0c41","tid":375500,"uid":102134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T19:11:46.000Z","msg":"澳門向賭場收錢再每年派錢比市民<br />\n其實已經係共業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}